# C++23 project — use "Latest" so clang-format understands the newest syntax.
# On clang-format 18 (ubuntu-latest) this resolves to C++20; upgrade clang-format
# to 19+ when Cpp23 becomes a valid enum value.
BasedOnStyle: Google
Standard: Latest
ColumnLimit: 100
IndentWidth: 2
TabWidth: 2
UseTab: Never
---
